# IPL Data Analysis Dashboard 🏏

## Overview
Analysis of IPL matches from 2008 to 2024 using Python, Pandas and NumPy.

## Key Findings
- Mumbai Indians are the most successful team with 140+ wins
- Virat Kohli is the all-time top scorer with 8014 runs
- YS Chahal is the highest wicket taker
- CH Gayle hit the most sixes in IPL history
- AB de Villiers won the most Player of the Match awards

## Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib

